      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A we'll attended meeting Of Spo-\nkane women interested in making\na concerted demonstration in be-\nhalf of the fair sex at the Spokane\nInterstate Fair, Tuesday. October\n4, which will be known as Women's\nDay, is being held this afternoon\nat the public library. Almost\nevery woman's club of any import\nance in the city was represented\nat the conference which was called\nat the suggestion Of r. H. Cos\ngrove, secretary and manager of\nthe fair\n\n\nAmong other things it is pro-\nposed to make the men folks take\nnotice through the medium Of a\nhuge parade in which will be sew\neraf original floats strongly empha-\nsizing woman's position in modern\nsociety.\n\n\n{ The Spokan Press, Delivered, for\nrs Cents Month."
    }
  ]
